trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte de tempo de criação num designer visual para o <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl"> </xref> controlo.

trans-unit.source: The HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner class is a base class for deriving your own data source designer for a custom data source control derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl> class.
trans-unit.target: A classe de HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner é uma classe base para efetuar a derivação o seus próprios estruturador de origens de dados para um controlo de origem de dados personalizados derivado de <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl>classe.</xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl>

trans-unit.source: Other classes that derive from HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner are <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Outras classes que derivem de HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner são <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de lista de ação para o estruturador do controlo.

trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.Configure*>método pode ser chamado.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.Configure*>

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.DataSourceChanged"></xref> event when the properties of the data source have changed and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*> property value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gera o <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.DataSourceChanged"> </xref> evento quando as propriedades da origem de dados foram alterados e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>valor da propriedade é <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>

trans-unit.source: The OnDataSourceChanged method notifies the designer of each control bound to the associated data source to refresh its control in the design host.
trans-unit.target: O método OnDataSourceChanged notifica o estruturador de cada controlo vinculado a origem de dados associada para atualizar o seu controlo no anfitrião de design.

trans-unit.source: This method can be suppressed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A> method, or by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> method with an argument of `false`.
trans-unit.target: Este método pode ser suprimido com o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>método, ou ao chamar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A>método com um argumento de `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.EventArgs> object provided by the calling object.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SchemaRefreshed"></xref> event when the schema of the data source has changed and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*> property value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gera o <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SchemaRefreshed"> </xref> eventos quando o esquema da origem de dados foi alterado e o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>valor da propriedade é <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>

trans-unit.source: This method notifies the designers of each control bound to the associated data source that the fields in the schema have changed.
trans-unit.target: Este método notifica os designers de cada controlo vinculado à origem de dados associado que alteraram os campos no esquema.

trans-unit.source: This method can be suppressed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A> method, or by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> method with an argument of `true`.
trans-unit.target: Este método pode ser suprimido com o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>método, ou ao chamar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A>método com um argumento de `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>
